article.title: Naval Network Warfare Assigns New Commanders
article.author: Henry Kenyon
article.text: Rear Adm. Thomas P. Meek, USN, has been assigned as commander, Navy Cyber Forces, and Rear Adm. Edward H. Deets III, USN, has taken command of the Naval Network Warfare Command at Joint Expeditionary Base Little Creek-Fort Story, Norfolk, Virginia.
